<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") -%>

<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 px-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">Cancellation & Refund Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted small">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            
            <div class="legal-content fs-6 lh-lg">
                <div class="alert alert-info border-0 rounded-4 p-4 mb-5" style="background-color: #f0f7ff;">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 text-primary">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-clock-rotate-left fs-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">30-Minute Grace Period</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-dark">We offer a <span class="fw-bold">50% refund</span> if you cancel your reservation within <span class="fw-bold text-primary">30 minutes</span> of booking. This gives you time to correct any accidental bookings or sudden plan changes.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">1. Refund Eligibility</h4>
                    <p>To be eligible for a partial refund, the following criteria must be met:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2">
                        <li>The cancellation must occur within <span class="fw-bold">30 minutes</span> from the time of booking confirmation.</li>
                        <li>The total booking price must be <span class="fw-bold text-success">greater than ₹500</span>.</li>
                        <li>The refund amount will be exactly <span class="fw-bold">50% of the total paid amount</span>.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">2. Non-Refundable Scenarios</h4>
                    <p>Bookings are <span class="fw-bold text-danger">non-refundable</span> in the following cases:</p>
                    <ul class="mt-2">
                        <li>Cancellation occurs more than 30 minutes after booking.</li>
                        <li>The total booking price is ₹500 or less.</li>
                        <li>The host has already initiated the check-in process (where applicable).</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">3. How to Cancel</h4>
                    <p>You can cancel your booking directly from your <a href="/bookings" class="fw-bold text-brand">My Trips</a> dashboard. If eligible, the refund will be automatically calculated and displayed before you confirm the cancellation.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">4. Refund Processing</h4>
                    <p>Once a refund is initiated, it typically takes <span class="fw-bold">5-7 business days</span> for the amount to reflect in your original payment method, depending on your bank or card issuer.</p>
                </section>
                
                <section class="mb-5">
                  <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">5. Host Cancellations</h4>
                  <p>In the rare event that a host cancels your booking, you will receive a <span class="fw-bold text-success">100% full refund</span> to your original payment method immediately.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
